From: Eryone X400 Migration <noreply@example.com>
Date: Thu, 15 May 2026 00:00:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] klippy: reduce queue logger retention

Legacy X400 patch reduced queue logger retention from 5 files to 1 file.
This is tracked as a temporary patch artifact; long-term, logging policy
belongs in deployment-level config.
---
 klippy/queuelogger.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/klippy/queuelogger.py b/klippy/queuelogger.py
index c6447f8..7606250 100644
--- a/klippy/queuelogger.py
+++ b/klippy/queuelogger.py
@@ -24,7 +24,7 @@ class QueueHandler(logging.Handler):
 class QueueListener(logging.handlers.TimedRotatingFileHandler):
     def __init__(self, filename):
         logging.handlers.TimedRotatingFileHandler.__init__(
-            self, filename, when='midnight', backupCount=5)
+            self, filename, when='midnight', backupCount=1)
         self.bg_queue = queue.Queue()
         self.bg_thread = threading.Thread(target=self._bg_thread)
         self.bg_thread.start()
